==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pitman
<hw>Pit"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Pitmen</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who works
in a pit, as in mining, in sawing timber, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>The connecting rod in a sawmill;
also, sometimes, a connecting rod in other machinery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>piton</ent>⟦br⟧
